---
title: Quick Double Korean Ginger Beef & Sesame Pear Slaw Bowl with Parsley & Crispy Shallots
description: Creamy slaw has just been upgraded to fruitalicious levels of flavour with the addition of pear tossed in sesame oil. Even
the beef strips are levelling up by cooking up a Korean sauce. There’s a sneaky bonus of ginger in there, you can thank us
later for that!
